node.text:
What a day!! The celebration of “a mural of hope and healing” by @evgola took place at Mixon Liquor in the heart of downtown San Diego. Thank you to all that showed your support! Special thanks to @craig.aerialcanvas for the amazing footage and @cbs8 for the coverage. Great pizza and drinks were enjoyed by all courtesy of our friends from @myyardlive @dangbrotherpizza 🙏🏽
#trustmevodka #mural #sandiego
#sandiegomurals #sandiegostreetart

Mixon Liquor

Stop by and purchase her gold flake bottles. Today only!!!
*While supplies last 
@craig.aerialcanvas 🎥
#trustmevodka #sandiego #sandiegomurals #murals #sandiegoliving
